&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;seeking&amp;nbsp;a highly experienced and collaborative&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Lead Engineer, Game Systems&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;to help drive the design, architecture, and implementation of core gameplay, progression, and economy systems. As&amp;nbsp;Lead&amp;nbsp;Engineer, Game Systems, you are passionate about developing scalable, performant, and engaging systems that empower designers and enhance the player experience.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Direct&amp;nbsp;a team of gameplay engineers and&amp;nbsp;work closely with design, production, and other engineering teams to bring a rich, responsive, and immersive world to life.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
