&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Work with our publishing partners to oversee the critical path for the&amp;nbsp;imprint program.&amp;nbsp;This includes providing&amp;nbsp;oversight to internal and external teams in Editorial, Managing Editorial,&amp;nbsp;Production,&amp;nbsp;and Art, ensuring alignment, efficiency, and financial discipline.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
